{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">They replaced the old world with a new one, a better one.</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/ec_steam_page_banner_about_english.png?t=1728403619\" /><br>As wars tore the globe apart and overpopulation pushed humanity to the brink, a lifeline emerged: The Arcade, a virtual world offering escape. In this digital utopia, everything is vibrant and shiny, everything runs smoothly... or so we\u2019ve been led to believe.<br>Mika never trusted The Arcade\u2019s ads, but her parents did. Hoping for a better life, they left without an explanation. Now, she\u2019s stepping into The Arcade to find them and uncover the truth behind its glossy facade.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/extra_coin_gif_1.gif?t=1728403619\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/ec_steam_page_banner_features_english.png?t=1728403619\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Delve into The Arcade city</strong></h2>Explore the streets of this virtual world to discover everything it has to offer. From die hard duelists to lazyheads, you\u2019ll find a unique crowd of people living here. Just be careful not to touch them in any way, it might trigger unwanted bugs.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/extra_coin_gif_2.gif?t=1728403619\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>New day new loop</strong></h2>Every day is a loop, giving you the freedom to spend your time and choose your activities as you see fit. Fancy a movie night or a gym session or maybe a duel? The Arcade has a spot for it all. However, keep in mind that slacking off won\u2019t go unnoticed; not everyone appreciates a lack of enthusiasm.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/extra_coin_gif_3.gif?t=1728403619\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Duel your way up</strong></h2>Climb the leaderboard of The Arcade by engaging in spectacular boss battles where you can enhance your strategy with up to 50 ultimates and 60 abilities. Who knows, maybe one loop you\u2019ll be one of those champions like the ones you see on the megascreens.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/extra_coin_gif_4.gif?t=1728403619\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Keep yourself busy with activities</strong></h2>The Arcade is brimming with things to do, with new minigames around every corner of the city. No time will be wasted because even something as simple as playing dice with a cat can boost a useful stat.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/extra_coin_gif_5.gif?t=1728403619\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Find. Your. Parents.</strong></h2>It won\u2019t be easy in a world where everyone looks the same and real names are erased by decree. Mika must uncover leads and seek allies in a place where trust seems like a distant illusion. To reunite with her family, she\u2019ll need to confront her deepest fears and doubts, pushing through a web of deception and uncertainty.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Family quarrel","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1290980/ae70d05cef1aa478c366c65b3822abd70be9b091.jpg"},{"name":"Gotta pet them all!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1290980/0fb41c95990a31c1e6a262b914e3f638c91324aa.jpg"},{"name":"D\u00e9j\u00e0 vu","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1290980/7ba35f81a2e4efde783232947a4de66cec06bd33.jpg"},{"name":"Mei Wong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/ima